title: Into the Night
description: The disappearance of a young woman from Bend, Oregon leads to an intense manhunt after the suspect sets off on a two state crime spree. Keith Morrison reports on the latest updates in the case. Originally aired on NBC on May 19, 2019.
author: nbcnews.podcasts@gmail.com (NBC News)
